{"tid":2152312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"出口美國的香港貨品須標明「中國」來源地      中華廠商會：影響不大","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T02:30:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b97453933a3e063ed6b9d0fdcd79a00012c3c37","tid":2152312,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:16:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543246-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543246-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=f145ba89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543246-20200812.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cdad986d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543246-20200812.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n美國宣布從9月25日開始，由香港出口至美國的貨品必須標明來源地是「中國」。<br />\n<br />\n中華廠商會聯合會會長吳宏斌認為影響不大，雖然香港製造會較吃香，但中國製造並非不值錢，又說中國是其中一個很受歡迎的產地，口碑很好，比東南亞更優勝，他認為美國的做法是政治原因大於一切。<br />\n<br />\n吳宏斌在本台節目《千禧年代》表示，大多數本港廠家在海外都有設廠，而且相關品牌屬於香港，只是產地來源有變更，他認為全球仍有百多個國家，市場很大。"},{"pid":"0793edf7da0be77c44928494a5838dfb7e1a4bc9","tid":2152312,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"但成個政府驚到震喎<br />\n林奠解釋下好喎"},{"pid":"919da0ce2de9ee11479d2f3209c03da331adb428","tid":2152312,"uid":68080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:25:34.000Z","msg":"咁唔需要反對啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf39c347d35f9896cd3b87952256dcc5691d6244","tid":2152312,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"你問班共狗<br />\n支共殺佢全家佢都係話影響不大㗎啦<br />\n比廢話更廢"},{"pid":"b744ca7767be7e3f4257f33310afa6e3b822c234","tid":2152312,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:26:36.000Z","msg":"一時又好大<br />\n一時又要反制<br />\n一時就無影響<br />\n究竟講緊乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57338c00f046375419d62918d307f218119215d","tid":2152312,"uid":266617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持one支那"},{"pid":"81e3f4c53783f8054eb16096d0ebe0ecd94d2f0f","tid":2152312,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:30:52.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">中國製造並非不值錢</span><br />\n<br />\n依家問題係你啲貨無人要，你整咁多出黎煲醋咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}